name: Josh Baker
bio:
Joshua is a junior majoring in Computer Science and is currently interning at
			   Enseo, Inc. in the quality assurance department. He has a natural interest in AI,
			   as it relates to many of his most significant interests, including technology,
			   philosophy, and politics. In his free time, he likes to write code, play videogames
			   , debate strangers on the internet, and hang out with friends.
